graph TD
    subgraph Signal_Layer [Stack 3: Visibility & Telemetry]
        A[Sentinel KQL Alert] -->|Trigger| B[Logic App / Webhook]
    end

    subgraph Orchestration_Layer [Modernization Atlas]
        B --> C{Risk Evaluation}
        C -->|High Risk| D[Enforcement Orchestrator]
        C -->|Low/Med| E[Notify MS Teams for Review]
    end

    subgraph Enforcement_Layer [Stack 2: Network & Device]
        D --> F[Palo Alto Panorama: Update DAG]
        D --> G[Cisco vManage: Quarantine Policy]
        F --> H[Immediate Session Block]
        G --> I[VLAN Isolation]
    end

    style D fill:#f96,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
